title: I AM ATHLETE | Will Smith Slaps Chris Rock: Was He Right or Wrong?

I AM ATHLETE | Episode 26
Chad "Ochocinco" Johnson, Pacman Jones, D.J. Williams and Omar Kelly discuss the Will Smith and Chris Rock slapping Incident at the 2022 Oscars in Episode 26 of I Am Athlete. Watch and listen as they share their thoughts, personal experiences and what they think is next for Will Smith and his family.
